{
  "texts": [
    "All interviews were held in English.",
    "As nearly all participants preferred an online interview over a face-toface interview, we decided to do all interviews via Zoom.",
    "All interviews were recorded with both sound and video.",
    "They varied in length from 30 to 45 minutes.",
    "During the interviews, the moderator made notes to write down any important followup questions and comments.While the interviews were carried out in a conversational style, i.e., rather informal and open-ended, we still followed our interview guide."
  ]
}